 field commutators or not, especially when the\nboundaries are modelled as perfect reflectors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Feb 2019 00:14:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Sep 2019 14:47:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-18"}
